    "citation" : "M. Roxana Sierra-Hernández, Paolo Gabrielli, Emilie Beaudon, Anna Wegner, Lonnie G. Thompson. 2018. Atmospheric depositions of natural and anthropogenic trace elements on the Guliya ice cap (northwestern Tibetan Plateau) during the last 340 years. Atmospheric Environment, 176, 91-102. doi: 10.1016/j.atmosenv.2017.11.040",
